{"ID":"20260305082130-d3wco14","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-d3wco14","tags":"课程/CPP程序设计","title":"类的静态成员","type":"doc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082201-ft0k23g","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082201-ft0k23g"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eWFtbA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"---\ntags:\n  - 课程/CPP程序设计\ntitle: 类的静态成员\ndate created: 星期六, 十月 18日 2025, 5:09:31 下午\ndate modified: 星期三, 十月 22日 2025, 5:19:22 下午\n---"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-4m0d96p","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-4m0d96p","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1 概述"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-x2n425z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-x2n425z","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"关键字："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"static"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\u003cfont color=\"#d83931\"\u003e静态成员是针对于类本身，而不是实例\u003c/font\u003e。分为两类："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-eea9ctk","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-eea9ctk","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-n50y2o7","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-n50y2o7","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-hhhyop0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-hhhyop0","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"静态数据成员：不同对象的静态数据成员共享存储同一空间；对象的存储空间中，不包含静态数据成员。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-af1gxfm","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-af1gxfm","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-8ibasg1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-8ibasg1","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"静态函数成员：无对象的地址，即无隐含参数 this；只能访问静态成员，调用静态函数成员。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-hc3znyr","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-hc3znyr","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2 静态数据成员"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-zeaddvh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-zeaddvh","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"静态数据成员 vs 普通数据成员："}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-u0xwq17","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-u0xwq17","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-fmvzsav","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-fmvzsav","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-1umzi54","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-1umzi54","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"作用域、访问权限无差别；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-75y3cgp","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-75y3cgp","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-k5p9bnb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-k5p9bnb","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"空间分配、生命周期不同；"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-24c5qko","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-24c5qko","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"常用于：用于描述类的总体信息，如对象总数、连接所有对象的链表表头等。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-hi6go66","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-hi6go66","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"静态数据成员只能定义一次（即使在多个文件中），其值\u003cfont color=\"#d83931\"\u003e在多个文件间共享\u003c/font\u003e。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-3znp24i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-3znp24i","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"非 const 静态数据成员需要在类体内声明，在类体外定义并初始化，也不能在函数体前初始化。在构造函数中，可以给静态数据成员赋值，但不称为初始化。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-mgi93rk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-mgi93rk","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3 静态函数成员"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-52bommg","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-52bommg","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-219tdr3","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-219tdr3","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-xppubgy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-xppubgy","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"普通函数成员的第一个参数是隐含 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"this"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 指针，指向调用该函数的对象；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ytvy8h7","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ytvy8h7","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-yy7zshn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-yy7zshn","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"静态函数成员没有 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"this"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 指针，因而通常需要用显式的参数来代替隐含的 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"this"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 指针；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-h0pm7aa","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-h0pm7aa","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-uag93f6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-uag93f6","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"若无参数，只应访问类的静态数据成员和静态函数成员；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-hgd5yl8","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-hgd5yl8","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-tuy0if1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-tuy0if1","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不能用 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"static"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 定义 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"block-ref","TextMarkBlockRefID":"20260305082130-gf29u2c","TextMarkBlockRefSubtype":"s","TextMarkTextContent":"虚函数"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"block-ref","TextMarkBlockRefID":"20260305082130-u04dh19","TextMarkBlockRefSubtype":"s","TextMarkTextContent":"关于 this 指针"}]}]}]}]}